						               													<description>&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#173;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#186;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#138;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#168;&amp;#232;&amp;#158;&amp;#162;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#174;&amp;#231;&amp;#137;&amp;#169;&amp;#232;&amp;#170;&amp;#158;&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#128;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#168;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#148;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#189;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#188;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#137;2&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;&amp;#231;&amp;#169;&amp;#162;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#181;&amp;#227;&amp;#131;&amp;#172;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#183;&amp;#229;&amp;#176;&amp;#145;&amp;#229;&amp;#185;&amp;#180; (Story of KIZUNA and &amp;quot;Luciola cruciata&amp;quot; - Episode 2: Soul Stained Juvenile) is an expansion to Story of KIZUNA and &quot;Luciola cruciata&quot;. It contains 10 new scenarios, 10 new characters, and some replacement cards for the characters in Episode 1. Some of the new scenarios and characters are of a new attribute, Dark. Also included are additional materials for making custom scenarios and characters, as well as new rules and mechanics regarding the use of enemies / ORs in the new scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Awakened from a long slumber, a boy sets out for a war to know the truth. This is a story of the boy getting back his life tainted by insane gods.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Three months have passed since &amp;quot;Luciola cruciata&amp;quot; stopped Old Rebellion's invasion into the human world through the gate, which was later called Voidgate Disaster. While people are regaining composure, in a facility of Luciola cruciata, a boy woke up from a 13-year sleep, which triggers the story to proceed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game expands the base game of Story of KIZUNA and &amp;quot;Luciola cruciata&amp;quot; with new scenarios and new characters. It also enables you to create your own characters and scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Publisher's summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
